{"tid":825163,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【二手冰河】太古城減價370萬求售 放4個月賣唔郁","createTime":"2018-09-17T11:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T07:46:17.000Z","uid":174649,"like":92,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"bbb77b5ca1abc3994f38004d64b03f53ae5104da","tid":825163,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T11:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180917/large/1537183146_b0ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180917%2Flarge%2F1537183146_b0ce.jpg&h=7e5d5164&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美聯物業吳肇基表示，二手交投非常慘淡，本月已經去到17號，鰂魚涌太古城仍只得1宗買賣，有機會創歷史先河，開始有業主減價，暫時最肯減的放盤，是翠榕閣高層E室，實用面積922方呎，三房間隔，望樓景，今年5月放盤，叫價2,230萬元，之後已減至1,950萬元，仍賣唔郁。<br />\n直至上月，同座樓上高層E室減價260萬至1,840萬元賣出，變成市價，業主終面對現實，現將叫價調低至1,860萬元求售，呎價20,174元，累減370萬元，較中銀及滙豐網上估值分別2,057萬及2,239萬元低最多379萬元或17%。"},{"pid":"9db19d3eb666321ab409b0797104caf457f40a32","tid":825163,"uid":120567,"like":193,"dislike":6,"score":187,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"啲樓都係有價無市，升值都係紙上盈利"},{"pid":"5239c8391f47205c890a241ad1c61f62460ca521","tid":825163,"uid":133641,"like":10,"dislike":117,"score":-107,"quote":{"pid":"9db19d3eb666321ab409b0797104caf457f40a32","tid":825163,"uid":120567,"like":193,"dislike":6,"score":187,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"啲樓都係有價無市，升值都係紙上盈利"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T11:51:48.000Z","msg":"講完後自我感覺良好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f810390dd594e79839e315b6ab654da80d66efa1","tid":825163,"uid":120567,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"5239c8391f47205c890a241ad1c61f62460ca521","tid":825163,"uid":133641,"like":10,"dislike":117,"score":-107,"quote":{"pid":"9db19d3eb666321ab409b0797104caf457f40a32","tid":825163,"uid":120567,"like":193,"dislike":6,"score":187,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T11:49:44.000Z",